# Cross-device sync (ADR 004). Optional — leave both unset and the app runs
# fully local, exactly as before. Set both to enable pairing + sync.
#
# Both are browser-public by design: security rests on RLS + the capability
# RPCs (get_progress / put_progress), which require the pairing code, not on
# secrecy of the anon key. See supabase/migrations/0001_progress_sync.sql and
# docs/runbooks.md.
#
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-public-anon-key
